{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KNQLcqFeq3jFdEFWKMKzhK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the current configuration:\n\n1. **systemLog.verbosity**: currently `1` → increase by 1 → set to `2`\n2. **operationProfiling.slowOpThresholdMs**: currently `200` → 2x → set to `400`\n3. **wiredTiger.engineConfig.journalCompressor**: currently `zlib` → change to `zstd`\n\nThe plan:\n1. Update the ConfigMap with the new values\n2. Perform a rolling restart of the StatefulSet to apply the changes\n3. Verify all members are healthy after the restart\n\nSince the StatefulSet uses `RollingUpdate` strategy with `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`, I can safely restart the pods while maintaining quorum—as long as at least 2 of the 3 members stay available, the replica set remains operational. I'll update the ConfigMap first, then trigger the rolling restart with `kubectl rollout restart`.\n\nThe changes I'm making to the MongoDB config are switching the journal compressor from zlib to zstd for better compression, increasing the log verbosity from 1 to 2 for more detailed logging, and raising the slow operation threshold from 200ms to 400ms to reduce noise in the logs.\n\nFor the rolling restart with this replica set, the `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` only affects how pods scale, not how they update. The `RollingUpdate` strategy with `partition: 0` means the StatefulSet will restart pods one at a time in reverse order (2, 1, 0), which should maintain quorum as long as the primary fails over correctly.\n\nI'll patch the ConfigMap, trigger the rollout restart, wait for completion, and verify the new configuration is applied. The WiredTiger journal compression change will take effect when mongod restarts with the new config from the ConfigMap—it's safe during a rolling restart since it only affects new journal files going forward.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":649,"cache_read_input_tokens":30905,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":649},"output_tokens":10,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9aabe326-b278-4bcc-a6e8-a2e8283b832e","uuid":"e24797ef-006c-45b7-a935-38898e9966dc","request_id":"req_011Ccf4xeD7SP3xZtVjtRTar"}
